				<h4>framework</h4>
				<p>The Artificial framework has three basic stylesheets, pulled in by framework.scss. These stylesheets, starting with the "artificial" prefix, specify the basic structure of the framework. These files should never be manipulated, and styles should be modified using .scss files with the "site" prefix.</p>
			</div>
